{"tid":1165655,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"輸入外勞被質疑易放難收 羅致光：人手緊張","createTime":"2019-05-22T02:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T02:48:53.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eae3cbb99dff3bf69cdf3977a1b0e840d2fdb572","tid":1165655,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%98%93%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%A3%E6%94%B6-%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-214500116.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258B%259E%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%2594%25B6-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2585%2589-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25B7%258A%25E5%25BC%25B5-214500116.html&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TQcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=2b95a10e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%98%93%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%A3%E6%94%B6-%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-214500116.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ywlLfiuqydyoe_XrL8yNGg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/b38d44d4b2c32f1002291655b00f6a89\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FywlLfiuqydyoe_XrL8yNGg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fb38d44d4b2c32f1002291655b00f6a89&h=1e312419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府指現時不少行業都面對招聘困難。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府及商界近日重提本港需輸入外勞補充人力短缺，勞工及福利局局長羅致光指現時不少行業都面對招聘困難，尤以安老及殘疾人士院舍人手最為短缺，當局下月會公布相關狀況，並研究是否輸入外勞。另外，社會福利署最快今年完成更新安老服務評估機制，羅致光強調更新機制對長者排隊輪候院舍服務及社區照顧服務並無影響。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光昨出席活動後被問到輸入外勞會否「易放難收」，他稱現時本港整體失業率為百分之二點八，而青年失業率約為百分之八，勞工市場較緊張，不少行業都難以請人。當局最關注安老及殘疾人士院舍行業的人手短缺問題，正在檢視改善院舍員工薪酬後的人手情況，會於一個多月後交代，當局又會研究各行業情況後考慮是否輸入外勞。<br />\n<br />\n又放150又引入外勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲嫌唔夠多人<br />\n難請人係睇下開咩價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab2a9b2dd83fbd97266bb0694ea18504bfb56dd","tid":1165655,"uid":221819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"好快150變1500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822b56ed2f69a5654c6a4d098613ddbc8487841b","tid":1165655,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:48:53.000Z","msg":"啲請人嘅人工待遇真係賤到，令我有一種「趕客」咁嘅感覺。"}]}